{"type":"message","id":"5e6ac072","parentId":"26ab0c37","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:10:54.957Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cFFlbV3O7h2L1L0GwPUSHobp","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":" ---\n\nUsage: okx account <action> [args...]\n\nAccount balance, positions, bills, and configuration.\n\nCommands:\n  balance              Get trading account balance\n                       Usage: okx account balance [<ccy>]\n\n  asset-balance        Get funding account asset balance\n                       Usage: okx account asset-balance [--ccy <ccy>]\n\n  positions            Get current open positions\n                       Usage: okx account positions [--instType <type>] [--instId <id>]\n\n  positions-history    Get historical positions\n                       Usage: okx account positions-history [--instType <type>] [--instId <id>] [--limit <n>]\n\n  bills                Get account bill history\n                       Usage: okx account bills [--instType <type>] [--ccy <ccy>] [--limit <n>] [--archive]\n\n  fees                 Get trading fee rates\n                       Usage: okx account fees --instType <type> [--instId <id>]\n\n  config               Get account configuration\n                       Usage: okx account config\n\n  set-position-mode    Set position mode (long/short or net)\n                       Usage: okx account set-position-mode --posMode <long_short_mode|net_mode>\n\n  max-size             Get maximum order size for an instrument\n                       Usage: okx account max-size --instId <id> --tdMode <cross|isolated> [--px <price>]\n\n  max-avail-size       Get maximum available tradable amount\n                       Usage: okx account max-avail-size --instId <id> --tdMode <cross|isolated|cash>\n\n  max-withdrawal       Get maximum withdrawable amount\n                       Usage: okx account max-withdrawal [--ccy <ccy>]\n\n  transfer             Transfer funds between accounts\n                       Usage: okx account transfer --ccy <ccy> --amt <n> --from <acct> --to <acct> [--transferType <0|1|2|3>]\n\n  audit                Audit account activity and tool call history\n                       Usage: okx account audit [--tool <name>] [--since <ISO-date>] [--limit <n>]\n\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"dawn-dune","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"\nUsage: okx [--profile <name>] [--demo] [--json] <module> <action> [args...]\n\nGlobal Options:\n  --profile <name>   Use a named profile from /home/zbb/.okx/config.toml\n  --demo             Use simulated trading (demo) mode\n  --json             Output raw JSON\n  --verbose          Show detailed network request/response info (stderr)\n  --version, -v      Show version\n  --help             Show this help\n\nModules:\n  market      Market data (ticker, orderbook, candles, trades)\n  account     Account balance, positions, bills, and configuration\n  spot        Spot trading (orders, algo orders)\n  swap        Perpetual swap trading (orders, algo orders)\n  futures     Futures trading (orders, positions, algo orders, leverage)\n  option      Options trading (orders, positions, greeks)\n  earn        Earn products — Simple Earn, On-chain Earn, and DCD (Dual Currency Deposit)\n  bot         Trading bot strategies (grid, dca)\n  config      Manage CLI configuration profiles\n  setup       Set up client integrations (Cursor, Windsurf, Claude, etc.)\n  diagnose    Run network / MCP server diagnostics\n\nRun \"okx <module> --help\" for module details.\n\n--- account ---\n\nUsage: okx account <action> [args...]\n\nAccount balance, positions, bills, and configuration.\n\nCommands:\n  balance              Get trading account balance\n                       Usage: okx account balance [<ccy>]\n\n  asset-balance        Get funding account asset balance\n                       Usage: okx account asset-balance [--ccy <ccy>]\n\n  positions            Get current open positions\n                 